                    "stepText": "Now, to maintain a continuous chain reaction at 50% of maximum potential, the absorption rate by the fuel must equal that by the moderator. Based on this, select the formula that correctly relates the number of moderator atoms ($!$N_{mod}$!$) to the number of thorium atoms ($!$N_{Th}$!$) using their respective absorption cross-sections.",
